 powers to push/pull/crash objects with your other one and collect enough points to reach the top of a worldwide leaderboard.", "short_description": "The only Infinite Run game in VR!\n\nChallenge your friends in an infinite run gameplay and see who emerges victorious. Enter a cyberpunk world and enjoy multiple game modes:\n\nMultiplayer Mode\nCampaign Mode\nDual Wield Mode\nBrisk Mode\n\nFuture! In the wake of a cataclysm! You are the prey in a world full of hunters. Be the last stand in an infinite run gameplay by starting with a simple blade and evolve to unlock more advanced weapons."}]}, "developer_name": "Outerlynx", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://outerlynx.com/brisk-square/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Outerlynx", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://outerlynx.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "8025128574236246"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572948_513498760027349_4846152387108758934_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FUmP8yDHMFYQ7kNvgE2shRW&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AAxVWkCPByOI5NsqgaeQd_V&oh=00_AYCT6aPWB09q64DC6ofCfNHv8LPAUIjiRWeWpnYn3OvKTg&oe=66E2C2B5"}, "is